  <brief_title>Stress Management Training for School Staff</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Efficacy of Using Blended Learning With the Stress Management and Resilience Training (SMART) Program to Decrease Stress and Enhance Resilience in Public School Staff</official_title>
  <sponsors>
